column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column4: Even though a lot of the varnish etc. seems like it's spray painted, the look of this lamp is great and it's excellent for the price. It was surprisingly easy to install, and it came with a yellow Wipro LED bulb. It immediately converted my small-ish room into a cosy looking space. The durability of the set up remains to be seen. Also the adjustable rod which connects the shade to the body stays just slightly tilted where the screw meets and pushes on to the rod. It's noticeable but can be ignored for an otherwise decent lamp you're getting at INR 1300.

column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column2: Excellent body of lamp but comes with a bad quality bulb.
column4: Excellent body of the lamp. I loved it. But the bulb used is a local product. Its actually a multi colored LED bulb which came faulty. I didn't want to replace the whole thing just for a faulty bulb. Then I couldn't find a new bulb in local shops nearby since it's not easily available. Then one god electrician came to rescue who fixed the bulb to atleast run in single white color. And that's how I managed to make the lamp work for me.Phewww..Thanks

column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column2: A note from the happy customer!üòä
column4: Initially we had trouble installing the lamp, as the lampshade was not being fitted properly. Then I remembered that there was a sweet note from the seller having their contact info. So I messaged them and what a service we received from a small scale vendor having a capacity of 5/6 people !!! They not only sent the demo video but also did a video call and explained thoroughly. This is the kind of service we expect, specially in this tough time when your movements are restricted.Now about the lamp! This is definitely one of the best I have ever purchased. It is simple, Sophisticated and thus, elegant. Gives a dreamy illumination. Unlike big vendors they also provide the bulb along with the lamp.Go for it guys , this is just worth buying. Yes, we had little trouble installing the lampshade but their service absolutely made it up.Paanch chamakte sitaara for Paradise Nauticals üòä!

column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column2: Good lamp, packaging should be way better.
column4: Its a beautiful lamp. Good finish on the product.The only problem was how the packaging was handled. I received with the bulb wire damaged and split into two parts.The seller just needs to find a packaging way so that the wire would not get damaged during the delivery. Thankfully we had an electritian who was able to fix this for us, so I cancelled the replacement request.Also, I was hoping to get a warm white bulb with it, which I did not. I would have preferred that.Overall its an amazing lamp for this 1450/- price range.

column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column4: The floor lamp is of very superior quality and truly meeting my needs. I am very much impressed about it's classic appearance, especially the wooden tripod stand and copper union which allows to increase the height of the light by atleast one feet. Only thing I have to say negative is the quality of the combo bulb which was a local make and the base of it became loose after two three times of fitting and removal. But that is a minor issue, when comparing with the quality of the floor lamp, which is of excellent quality. I give five stars for the product and value for money because it deserves to be given.

column1: SIMRAN HANDICRAFTS Metal, Wood Lamp, Bronze,Pack of 1
column4: I‚Äôm so glad I went for this lamp !! Really pretty, livens up the place, even during daylight. The quality of components is good too, the legs are made of proper wood and are sturdy, the rest of the product is good as well. Moreover, there‚Äôs hardly any assembly required, just fix the lamp shade, screw in the bulb (included with the product) and you‚Äôre set. Very reasonably priced too, complete value for my money. But the best bit though, the manufacturer, Paradise Nauticals, is a small, nay, micro  business venture of just 5-6 people; and they‚Äôve come up with a quality product, kudos to them !!
